
## Rollcall vote data for 114th Senate {.unnumbered}


### Description

This rollcall vote object (see <code>rollcall</code>) contains voting records for the 114th Senate in the US
Congress. Not all rollcalls are included, only those that had a 70-30 or closer split in the vote.
The data can be pre-processed via the <code>id_make</code> function for estimation. 
See package vignette for details.



### Usage

<pre><code class='language-R'>senate114
</code></pre>


### Format

A long data frame with one row for every vote cast by a Senator.
